    "  <button class='btn btn-success'>Success</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-warning'>Warning</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-danger'>Danger</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-info'>Info</button>",
    "</div>",
    
    "<h3 style='margin-top: 2rem;'>Tama√±os de Botones</h3>",
    "<p>Tres tama√±os: peque√±o, normal y grande.</p>",
    "<div class='og-flex og-wrap og-gap-md' style='margin-bottom: 1rem; align-items: center;'>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>Peque√±o</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-primary'>Normal</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-primary btn-lg'>Grande</button>",
    "</div>",
    
    "<h3 style='margin-top: 2rem;'>Botones Outline</h3>",
    "<p>Variante con fondo transparente y borde de color.</p>",
    "<div class='og-flex og-wrap og-gap-md' style='margin-bottom: 1rem;'>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-outline btn-primary'>Primary Outline</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-outline btn-secondary'>Secondary Outline</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-outline btn-success'>Success Outline</button>",
    "</div>",
    
    "<h3 style='margin-top: 2rem;'>Estados de Botones</h3>",
    "<p>Botones con estados interactivos: loading, processing, success, error.</p>",
    
    "<h4 style='margin-top: 1rem;'>Estado Loading (rayas animadas)</h4>",
    "<div class='og-flex og-wrap og-gap-md' style='margin-bottom: 1rem;'>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-primary btn-loading'>Cargando...</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-success btn-loading'>Guardando...</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-danger btn-loading'>Eliminando...</button>",
    "</div>",
    
    "<h4 style='margin-top: 1rem;'>Estado Processing (puntos animados)</h4>",
    "<div class='og-flex og-wrap og-gap-md' style='margin-bottom: 1rem;'>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-primary btn-processing'>Procesando</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-info btn-processing'>Conectando</button>",
    "</div>",
    
    "<h4 style='margin-top: 1rem;'>Estados Temporales (success/error)</h4>",
    "<div class='og-flex og-wrap og-gap-md' style='margin-bottom: 1rem;'>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-success-temp'>Guardado ‚úì</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-error-temp'>Error ‚úï</button>",
    "</div>",
    
    "<h4 style='margin-top: 1rem;'>Bot√≥n Deshabilitado</h4>",
    "<div class='og-flex og-wrap og-gap-md' style='margin-bottom: 1rem;'>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-primary' disabled>Deshabilitado</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-secondary' disabled>No disponible</button>",
    "</div>",
    
    "<h3 style='margin-top: 2rem;'>Demo Interactiva - Estados</h3>",
    "<p>Haz clic en el bot√≥n para ver la transici√≥n de estados.</p>",
    "<div class='og-flex og-gap-md' style='margin-bottom: 1rem;'>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-primary' onclick='ejemplos.demoButtonStates(this)'>Enviar Formulario</button>",
    "  <button class='btn btn-danger' onclick='ejemplos.demoButtonError(this)'>Simular Error</button>",
    "</div>",
    
    "<h3 style='margin-top: 2rem;'>Button Groups (Radio Buttons Estilizados)</h3>",
    "<p>Grupos de botones donde solo uno puede estar seleccionado (radio buttons bajo el cap√≥).</p>",
    
    "<h4 style='margin-top: 1rem;'>Ejemplo 1: Selecci√≥n de Plan</h4>",
    "<div class='btn-group' role='group' style='margin-bottom: 1rem;'>",
    "  <input type='radio' name='plan' id='plan-basic' value='basic' class='btn-group-input' checked>",
    "  <label for='plan-basic' class='btn btn-group-item'>B√°sico</label>",
    "  ",
    "  <input type='radio' name='plan' id='plan-pro' value='pro' class='btn-group-input'>",
    "  <label for='plan-pro' class='btn btn-group-item'>Pro</label>",
    "  ",
    "  <input type='radio' name='plan' id='plan-enterprise' value='enterprise' class='btn-group-input'>",
    "  <label for='plan-enterprise' class='btn btn-group-item'>Enterprise</label>",
